{"product_id":"customize-your-wall-4-piece-split-art-set-2-2-grid","title":"Customize Your Wall 4 Piece Split Art Set (2×2 Grid)","description":"\u003ch2\u003e🖼️ 4-Piece Custom Poster Set (2×2 Split) – Made Just for You\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTurn your favorite memories, ideas, or inspirations into a stunning \u003cstrong\u003e4-piece wall art set\u003c\/strong\u003e. This custom split combo is designed to transform any space with a clean, balanced, and premium look—perfect for bedrooms, living rooms, gaming setups, offices, or gifting.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eUpload your own photo, artwork, quote, or design and we’ll professionally print it as a \u003cstrong\u003ematching 2×2 split poster set\u003c\/strong\u003e (4 panels) that looks cohesive and eye-catching on your wall.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e✨ Why You’ll Love It\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eFully \u003cstrong\u003ecustomizable\u003c\/strong\u003e – upload your own image or design\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ePrinted as a \u003cstrong\u003e4-piece coordinated 2×2 set\u003c\/strong\u003e for a clean gallery-style finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eHigh-quality print with rich colors and sharp details\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eLightweight, easy to paste, and wall-friendly\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eIdeal for \u003cstrong\u003epersonal décor, gifts, couple photos, memory walls, brand walls\u003c\/strong\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch3\u003e📐 Product Details\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eSet includes \u003cstrong\u003e4 individual posters\u003c\/strong\u003e (2×2 split layout)\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ePrinted on \u003cstrong\u003e300 GSM matte\u003c\/strong\u003e premium paper\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eFade-resistant, high-resolution printing\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ePerfect for bedrooms, halls, hostels, studios \u0026amp; offices\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cblockquote\u00